      • Transaction

        public Transaction(Node to,
                   java.lang.Double tokens)
        Constructor to create a Transaction object entity with all the required parameters and variables. It includes accurate dates from the moment to where a transaction is created to when it is expired. A transaction expires in 1 hour by default.
        Parameters:
        to - Receiver node ID
        tokens - Transaction recipient
